{"word":"συνιζάνω","slug":"συνιζάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνιζάνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to sink in, collapse</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to sink</i>, of the wind, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}